column5: I really need to fish for these things before I get too old!!!!  https://www.facebook.com/AssassinJigTeam/videos/926975060691784/
Wow...something tells me its already too late
Not quite the same thrill as Simcoe 'jumbo perch"!!
Not quite the same thrill as Simcoe 'jumbo perch"!!  Not quite. When that thing took off it was like he hooked a passing train!!!
I caught a Bat Ray that was almost in the same setting. I'm just glad I didn't step on it first.
True bucket list fish!   These are just babies,
I'd have to get back into the Gym and train like a warrior to take one on.
